HEADWORD: Guileful
<hw>Guile"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Full of guile;
characterized by cunning, deceit, or treachery; guilty.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Guile"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Guile"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
